'''Cannabis in the United Arab Emirates''' is illegal. Even the smallest amounts of the drug can lead to a mandatory four-year prison sentence.<ref>{{cite news |url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/uk/7234786.stm |title = UAE Drug Laws |publisher = BBC News |date = 8 February 2008 |accessdate = 2011-02-17 }}</ref>

==Economy==
The UAE is not a significant cannabis producer or consumer, but is a major transshipment point for cannabis from Pakistan and Afghanistan, due to its free ports and heterogeneous population.<ref name="Maisel">{{cite book|author=Sebastian Maisel|title=Saudi Arabia and the Gulf Arab States Today: An Encyclopedia of Life in the Arab States|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=uhJu2_8vMkMC&pg=PA124|publisher=Greenwood Press|isbn=978-0-313-34442-8|pages=124–}}</ref>

